  "detailed_description": "Primordial Pain is a brutally unforgiving, fast paced arena shooter with one key mechanic:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/124b03bf0c0ad5efb655477bf2a88dc1.avif?t=1667248141\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>Pain serves both as your health and as a multiplier for your damage output.<br>While playing you're constantly performing an elegant dance on the fine line of maximum power and certain death.<br>To defeat the primordial horrors that lurk in the darkness and overcome the pain you must perfect the dance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/bd851978026bf2775c960c794a93834a.poster.avif?t=1667248141\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/bd851978026bf2775c960c794a93834a.webm?t=1667248141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/bd851978026bf2775c960c794a93834a.mp4?t=1667248141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/35230dcd5e7b1e02bfd6cc69c6bc47f1.avif?t=1667248141\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>Primordial Pain constrains you to a seemingly small arena, provides you with various different movement options and proceeds to through waves of enemies at you each requiring a different strategy to defeat.<br>You will have to experiment with every single mechanic at your disposal to discover optimal strategies or you will get overwhelmed by hordes of adversaries.<br>Survive long enough and great ancient beasts will reveal themselves.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/860489ad86b9dc39402dc5408caedb1d.poster.avif?t=1667248141\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/860489ad86b9dc39402dc5408caedb1d.webm?t=1667248141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/860489ad86b9dc39402dc5408caedb1d.mp4?t=1667248141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/a7e32e50c96586187440d5005f9e8711.avif?t=1667248141\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>While playing you can either focus on surviving for as long as possible or to top your own highscore.<br>Whereas time constantly ticks up, your score depends on how quickly you can dispatch enemies as well as your method.<br>Playing in a stylish way will reward you with more points to be added to your score.",
  "about_the_game": "Primordial Pain is a brutally unforgiving, fast paced arena shooter with one key mechanic:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/124b03bf0c0ad5efb655477bf2a88dc1.avif?t=1667248141\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>Pain serves both as your health and as a multiplier for your damage output.<br>While playing you're constantly performing an elegant dance on the fine line of maximum power and certain death.<br>To defeat the primordial horrors that lurk in the darkness and overcome the pain you must perfect the dance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/bd851978026bf2775c960c794a93834a.poster.avif?t=1667248141\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/bd851978026bf2775c960c794a93834a.webm?t=1667248141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/bd851978026bf2775c960c794a93834a.mp4?t=1667248141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/35230dcd5e7b1e02bfd6cc69c6bc47f1.avif?t=1667248141\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>Primordial Pain constrains you to a seemingly small arena, provides you with various different movement options and proceeds to through waves of enemies at you each requiring a different strategy to defeat.<br>You will have to experiment with every single mechanic at your disposal to discover optimal strategies or you will get overwhelmed by hordes of adversaries.<br>Survive long enough and great ancient beasts will reveal themselves.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/860489ad86b9dc39402dc5408caedb1d.poster.avif?t=1667248141\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/860489ad86b9dc39402dc5408caedb1d.webm?t=1667248141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/860489ad86b9dc39402dc5408caedb1d.mp4?t=1667248141\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/a7e32e50c96586187440d5005f9e8711.avif?t=1667248141\" width=512 height=64 /></span><br>While playing you can either focus on surviving for as long as possible or to top your own highscore.<br>Whereas time constantly ticks up, your score depends on how quickly you can dispatch enemies as well as your method.<br>Playing in a stylish way will reward you with more points to be added to your score.",
